import { Component, EventEmitter, Input, Output } from '@angular/core';
import { Species } from '../../models';

@Component({
  selector: 'species-detail',
  templateUrl: 'species-detail.component.html',
})
export class SpeciesDetailComponent {

  @Input() public currentSpecies: Species;
  @Input() public speciesPlanet: string;
  @Output() public toggledChange: EventEmitter<number> = new EventEmitter<number>();

}

<div class="card">

    <div class="card-body" *ngIf="currentSpecies">
        <button type="button" class="close" aria-label="Close" (click)="toggledChange.emit(currentSpecies.id-1)">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
        <h5 class="card-title">Species details</h5>
        <div class="card-text">
        <p>Name: <b>{{currentSpecies.name}}</b></p>
        <p>Home planet: <b>{{speciesPlanet}}</b></p>
        <p>Classification: <b>{{currentSpecies.classification}}</b></p>
        <p>Language: <b>{{currentSpecies.language}}</b></p>

        </div>


    </div>
</div>
